	<LocalizedText>
		<Text id="LOC_DESCRIPTION">
			<en_US>
				This mod overhauls the mod manager screen.[NEWLINE][NEWLINE]The mod list is split between disabled and enabled mods making it easy to see which mods are active. It also includes a number of enhancements to the filtering and search options:[NEWLINE][NEWLINE]- Right Click Enable/Disable Mod[NEWLINE]- Hold shift to select multiple mods at once[NEWLINE]- Filter out mods that affect save games[NEWLINE]- Sort by Author[NEWLINE]- Sort by Dependency[NEWLINE]- Search by Name, Teaser or Author
			</en_US>
			<zh_Hans_CN>
				这个MOD彻底重做了MOD管理界面。[NEWLINE][NEWLINE]本MOD把已经启用的MOD和已经禁用的MOD分成两个部分，方便玩家管理，并且添加了一些增强的过滤和搜索功能。[NEWLINE][NEWLINE]- 右键启用/禁用MOD[NEWLINE]- 按住Shift一次选中多个MOD。[NEWLINE]- 过滤影响存档的MOD[NEWLINE]- 按照作者排序[NEWLINE]- 按照关联排序[NEWLINE]- 依照标题、描述或者作者来搜索MOD
			</zh_Hans_CN>
		</Text>
		<Text id="LOC_TEASER">
			<en_US>
